    <h1>Information safety and disinformation.</h1>
    <p class="lead">Disinformation targets communities that do not have a trusted, local source of truth. When a rumour or a manipulated claim spreads, and there is no calm, sourced place to turn, the loudest voice fills the gap. Indigenous communities are deliberately targeted, and the harm lands hardest where local, trusted information is thin. This whole hub is one answer to that. This page is the other: helping members recognize the tactic before it lands.</p>
